dc_description_s: New Building Locations points exported from the CIty's GIS. See summary description (txt) file for information about intended use, projection, currency, attributes, etc.This map data layer represents the new building locations for the City of Bloomington, Indiana. The new building locations points layer was created to supplement the Building Footprints map layer as a place holder where new buildings are approved or built but building footprint features are not yet digitized.
